    <TD VALIGN=top><DIV class="main"><STRONG><A NAME="harmonic minor"></A>The harmonic minor scale</STRONG>

<P>The harmonic minor scale has just one tonally effective mode and that is the scale conventionally known as the harmonic minor scale. It is spelled, in numerical form (relative to the major scale):</P>

